      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## CAT I Open-Findings War Room\nCAT I (severity **high**) are the findings that fail you at audit. Top row and left trends are **enterprise-wide** (all collections, from Prometheus history). The **live table** and per-collection trend on the right follow the **Collection** selector and hit the STIG Manager API directly for current rule detail.\n\n*Left/stats: Prometheus. Right table: Infinity (live).*"
